# go-openholidays code ownership.
#
# GitHub auto-requests review from the listed owner(s) for every PR that
# touches files matching the pattern. Patterns follow .gitignore syntax.
#
# Caveat: a bare handle (`@egeek-tech`) only auto-requests reviews when it
# resolves to a GitHub *user* account. For *organization* accounts the entry
# must be `@egeek-tech/<team-slug>` and that team must have write access to
# this repo. If review requests do not fire after a PR is opened, switch the
# entry to a team form.

# Catch-all — owns every path in the repo.
* @egeek-tech
